<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sardion Care</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/shrunk-logo.png" type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/FontAwesome/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/common.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/home.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/media-queries.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="hero" id="home">
                <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
                <div class="hero-text">
                    <div class="hero-text-box">
                        <h2>Help Children Reach Their Full Potential</h2>
                        <p>At the heart of our mission lies a simple but powerful belief: every child deserves a chance to pursue their dreams. our organization, Youth Empowerment Services <span class="highlight">Sardion Care</span>, is dedicated to transforming the lives of young people across the country. Through a range of innovative programs and services, we work to strengthen families, prevent youth from entering the juvenile justice system, and support children's mental health.
                            Whether you're a parent seeking support for your child, a community member looking to get involved, or a policymaker interested in improving outcomes for youth, YES is here to help. Join us in our mission to create a brighter future for all children.</p>
                        <a href="/about">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-slash">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" height="100px" viewBox="0 0 1280 140"
                        preserveAspectRatio="none">
                        <g fill="#87604f">
                            <path d="M1280 140V0H0l1280 140z" />
                        </g>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="about page" id="about">
                <div class="about-box">
                    <div class="about-left">
                        <div class="head">
                            <h1>Our Mission</h1>
                            <p>Our experience and research have taught us this: a family does a better job of
                                raising a child than the state. <span class="highlight">Sardion Care</span> provides and
                                advocates for innovative, evidence-based,
                                family-focused services designed to bring help and hope to children and their families,
                                as well as proven services for young adults turning 18 in foster care.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="about-right">
                        <div class="about-img">
                            <img src="/images/mission.jpg" alt="" id="abt-img-1">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="space"></div>
                <div class="about-box">
                    <div class="about-left about-hide">
                        <div class="about-img">
                            <img src="/images/vision.jpg" alt="" id="abt-img-2">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="about-right">
                        <div class="head">
                            <h1>Our Vision</h1>
                            <p><span class="highlight">Sardion Care</span> provides services in standard group care with
                                a strong emphasis on service
                                for high risk youth and large sibling groups: Placements for siblings in one home will
                                ensure the family connectives and we have several houses designed to provide a home for
                                siblings.We believe in the importance of skilled and therapeutic intervention to
                                stabilize behaviour; enhance the self-worth and dignity of each individual; and to
                                promote healing of childhood neglect, abuse and trauma by using holistic values.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="about-hidden">
                        <div class="about-img">
                            <img src="/images/vision.jpg" alt="" id="abt-img-2">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="believes" id="beliefs">
                <div class="believes-overlay page">
                    <div class="head">
                        <h1>Our Beliefs</h1>
                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>That children are a gift from the Creator</li>
                        <li>That our children have a right to live proudly as First Nations people in the lands of their
                            ancestors</li>
                        <li>That each child is part of what makes a community whole</li>
                        <li>That children, under the guidance of Elders, will learn to love learning throughout their
                            life</li>
                        <li>That children have a right to enjoy the opportunities that education offers</li>
                        <li>That children have a right to live in healthy, self-determining communities that are free of
                            violence</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="services page" id="services">
                <div class="head">
                    <h1>Some Of Our Services</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="services-holder">
                    <button class="services-next"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></button>
                    <button class="services-back"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i></button>
                    <div class="services-box">
                        <div class="services-slider">
                            <div class="service">
                                <img src="/images/service-1.jpg" alt="service">
                                <div class="service-overlay">
                                    <div class="service-text">
                                        <h1>Support</h1>
                                        <p>We offer crucial support to children who have experienced trauma or difficult family situations.To provide a stable, nurturing environment where children can receive the care and attention they need to heal and thrive.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="service">
                                <img src="/images/service-2.jpg" alt="service">
                                <div class="service-overlay">
                                    <div class="service-text">
                                        <h1>Adventure</h1>
                                        <p>We provide opportunities for children in care to experience new adventures and create happy memories. These experiences can help build confidence, develop new skills, and form positive connections.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="service">
                                <img src="/images/service-3.jpg" alt="service">
                                <div class="service-overlay">
                                    <div class="service-text">
                                        <h1>Road Trip</h1>
                                        <p>Road trips with can offer children a chance to bond, make new memories, and experience new places. These experiences can help create a sense of belonging and stability, building positive connections between children and society at large.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="service">
                                <img src="/images/service-4.jpg" alt="service">
                                <div class="service-overlay">
                                    <div class="service-text">
                                        <h1>Art</h1>
                                        <p>Children tend to use art as a way to express their feelings and cope with difficult situations.We can provide a safe and supportive environment for children to explore their creativity, promoting healing and emotional well-being.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <%- include('partials/contact') %>
</body>
<script src="/scripts/common.js"></script>
<script src="/scripts/home.js"></script>

</html>